{"id":590666,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【立此存照】性侵，是一个延续性动词（微博网友/","date":"2018-07-27T10:56:26Z","modified":"2018-07-27T17:22:25Z","title":"【立此存照】性侵，是一个延续性动词（微博网友书法、漫画作品汇总）","content":"<p>【编者按】尽管对#metoo、性侵等相关话题的讨论在大陆社交媒体受到审查和封杀，有心网友却巧妙借助书法、漫画等其他形式参与反性侵议题讨论。中国数字时代整理编辑了微博网友近期发布的作品，供读者参考。</p>\n<p><strong>微博@黑画笔Heihuabi：</strong>【性侵，是一个延续性动词】最近几天，越来越多被性侵的受害者鼓起勇气在网上发声。听到他们的声音，更意识到性侵所带来的伤害，会伴随受害者一生。无论你是男性还是女性，希望你都要保护好自己，遇到恶，不要沉默，让坏人接受他/她应有的惩罚。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/对性侵说不.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-590667\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/对性侵说不.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/对性侵说不.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/对性侵说不-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>微博@龙首常江：</strong>这几天的蜜兔事件，让这个话题再度热议。面对恶，我们要一起说“不”！愿遭受过性侵的人能走出阴影，阳光下才静好。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_590669\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-590669 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"660\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵2.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵2-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">对性侵说不 @龙首常江</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_590670\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-590670 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"660\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵3.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵3-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">对二次伤害说不 @龙首常江</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_590671\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵4.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-590671\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"660\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵4.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵4-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">男孩也要敢说不 @龙首常江</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_590672\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵5.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-590672\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"660\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵5.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵5-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">对沉默说不 @龙首常江</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_590673\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵6.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-590673\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"660\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵6.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/性侵6-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">对冷漠说不 @龙首常江</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>微博@甜到炸的少女宸：</strong>（摘抄《房思琪的初恋乐园》）原来，人对他者的痛苦是毫无想象力的。忍耐不是美德，把忍耐当成美德是这个伪善的世界维持他扭曲秩序的方式，生气才是美德。<br />\n<i class=\"W_icon ico_member3\"></i></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_590674\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-590674 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪1.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪1-300x243.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">“思琪，她真的爱过，她的爱只是失禁了，忍耐不是美德，把忍耐当成美德是这个伪善的世界维持它扭曲的秩序的方式。生气才是美德。”</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_590675\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-590675 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"371\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪2.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪2-300x253.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">“他发现社会对性的禁感太方便了。强暴一个女性，全世界都觉得是她自己的错，连她自己都觉得是自己的错。”</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_590676\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-590676 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪3.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/房思琪3-300x255.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">“她确确实实感觉到，心里有什么被他捅死，在她能够知道那个什么是什么之前就被捅死了。”</p></div>\n","author":1056,"categories":[18270,18269,27949],"tags":[33629,33760,33799,28641,26991,23557,29781]}